item.title: Cognitive Explorers
item.description: Master Thesis in Arts and Neurosciences - UFRJ 2017 Cognitive Explorers was an experiment run during my master thesis in Arts and Neurosciences. For it I created a custom made Virtual Reality experience to be used with Neurophysiological data in order to discover how complex emotions are processed in the brain.
